  <section class="enterprise-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">BUSINESS OF MEDICINE INTELLIGENCE</p><h1>A physician-first intelligence platform, built one protected decision at a time.</h1><p>BOMSociety helps physicians make better Business of Medicine decisions. Anonymous aggregate decision patterns can improve that guidance while enterprise support keeps physician access free.</p><p class="enterprise-status">STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT. Physicians remain free. Individual physician data is never sold.</p></div></section>
